"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Crypto exchanges aren't content to just suck up revenue from [Bitcoin](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-bitcoin-four-minute-instant-guide-explainer) and altcoin trades these days. They're charging hard into [NFT](https://decrypt.co/resources/non-fungible-tokens-nfts-explained-guide-learn-blockchain) trading.\\n\\nBlockchain.com, the wallet and trading platform led by CEO Peter Smith, today teased its marketplace for buying, selling, and holding [Ethereum](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-ethereum-quickly-explained-four-minute-guide)-based NFTs. The company says the feature will be available within weeks; it's currently taking waitlist signups.\\n\\n\\\"We want to make accessing the NFT market as easy as accessing the crypto market,\\\" reads a [press release](https://support.blockchain.com/hc/en-us/articles/360051018031-Technical-differences-between-the-Private-Key-Wallet-and-Trading-Account). \\\"With the Blockchain.com NFT marketplace (in beta), youâ€™ll be able to browse, buy, sell, and securely store NFTs without ever leaving your Blockchain.com Wallet.\\\" (Although users *can* leave; the wallet is non-custodial, meaning NFTs can be transferred to other wallets.)\\n\\nNFTs are digital proofs of ownership created with smart contracts on a blockchain such as Ethereum, [Flow](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-flow-dapper-labs), or [Solana](https://decrypt.co/resources/what-is-solana-a-scalable-decentralized-network-for-dapps). They are typically linked to digital art, collectibles, and audio files, but can also be tied to tangible objects.\",\"timestamp\":1638510709,\"title\":\"Coinbase and FTX, Opens NFT Marketplace\"},\"digest\":\"HiPOZEbjaNKynlO5cfEluu8vffjX1qwgPAMCFxffDYc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x68192171d7B4977Dca44f7eA5703866E038676a0\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"TwRFtR7A2zYowxy9Tykq8w9xZPUc15zhUV26uTzxHJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"WDRKLp8_LW_gM4Ogq2_WmCg11fljKzEXGptq_qvUjkg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"n2DXWDVS5r20_BS8sgID2s7fYtGdwrZkPDK6w2gofRsN1kdv7DCnqmfMliXUvHkkimZs6j0w3GTl_9kuiuG9iw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8689507f0b8f81ef353fd442d35c05b51131c24a7e3a2dc7f9bd436cf9ef217155daef3e97f61fc7847e16867c5c75b638d54db2bf9833571924cd9ce692a7e41b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"TwRFtR7A2zYowxy9Tykq8w9xZPUc15zhUV26uTzxHJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"WDRKLp8_LW_gM4Ogq2_WmCg11fljKzEXGptq_qvUjkg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"HiPOZEbjaNKynlO5cfEluu8vffjX1qwgPAMCFxffDYc\"}"